üîç Why your ‚ÄúMetrics‚Äù was highlighted

One of these was happening:

background-color set directly on .sidebar-item

.active class added by default in HTML

:focus or :active styling not cleared

routerLinkActive auto-adding class


üëâ This CSS neutralizes all of that


---

‚úÖ Rule of thumb

Hover ‚Üí handled by :hover

Selected ‚Üí YOU add .active

Default ‚Üí always transparent



